      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, it presents in showroom condition with an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior that remains indistinguishable from new. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly superlative example of engineering excellence.",
