      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's basically brand new and has been babied since day one. I'm talking pristine interior, flawless paint, and it drives like a dream! I hate to let it go, but I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
