    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction. This example features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power delivery through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-calibrated Variable M Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit longitudinal traction. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring mechanical longevity. Finished in Alpine White with a pristine Nappa leather interior, the factory aerodynamics and staggered Style 67 wheels remain in concours condition. No subframe hairline fractures, no rod bearing play, and zero pixel degradation in the instrument cluster\u2014a truly turnkey specimen of Bavarian performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Low mileage. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service records available.",
