    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most meticulous inspection. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and features a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and professional ceramic coating. There are absolutely no swirls, chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' aroma; the leather bolsters show zero signs of entry wear, and every electronic component operates with factory-spec precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment that drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
